messages.text: im going to skip our faculty meeting today
yeah. just don’t want to come in on a saturday again. wanted to do some cleaning
oh, i get that. i’ve already skipped two saturdays this school year so i think i’m locked in
i know i’ve said this a thousand times, but let me or any of the girls know if you ever need to talk
youre not alone. we’re your coworkers but we’re also your friends. you know that. its hard to bear a loss alone
I know. thanks for welcoming me back to work
well, I’m headed up to the attic
yikes. good luck up there. getting rid of some old junk?
yes. do you know anyone who might need baby clothes? they’ve never really been warn.
i know sweetie. im so sorry.
slow down. what’s happening?? do you need to come over? are you safe?
i don’t know oh my god
i went upstairs into the attic. its the first time i’ve been up there since...
nothing. i was going through bags of clothes, toys, baby shower gifts, cards, all the old stuff i put up there that i just couldn’t deal with looking at
maybe its too soon for that Talia
im trying to move on. move on. move on. i thought if i just gave things away to some charity or something it would be a good first step
i went through everything and put it in trash bags
and put them out on the street for salvation army to come pick up
sorry. that sounds traumatic. maybe you should keep one thing? a memento?
i went inside, decided to relax. pull it together. breathe.
and when i went to the door the bags were back
maybe someone just pulled them back up to your porch
so i put them back outside
and when i looked the bags were back
but don’t you think it was just a neighbor??
carmen. they were INSIDE the house
the bags were at the street and then they were in the front hall
did i hear the door open? no. did i hear anyone come inside? no. they just APPEARED.
don’t go jumping to conclusions tho girl
the clothes of my dead child keep showing up in my house. you think that’s some kind of neighborly coincidence?!?!?!!
i don’t know. all i’m saying is i know you’ve been in a bad place. do you think maybe you’re imagining things? or maybe you forgot bringing them back in?
maybe you came back to school too soon. maybe you need more time?
what?!??! come on. I just want you to consider that maybe its not what it looks like! this isn’t some ghost story talia! this is real life, ok?!?!? YOU NEED HELP.
because im sorry. im there for you. no matter what.
i just knew that i had to get rid of them. if i didn’t they would keep coming back
it was making me feel crazy
i did it and i was angry and scared and i regret it now
don’t be so hard on yourself. youre hurting
i regret it because something worse happened
just get out of that house!
you should not be alone right now
but it could be anyone!!! “im here”??? could be a repair man? pizza man? wrong number???? talia im getting worried. you want me to call someone? call your mother?
talia. she’s dead. im sorry but its true. you said it yourself you’re trying to move on
it wasn’t your fault! lots of babies just don’t wake up. theres even a name for it. it happens. im sorry but it happens and it wasn’t anything you did. she was so little.
then why did she send me this?
[FWD]: unknown sender: why didn’t you take care of me
jesus. someone is playing some sick joke
you need to call the police
but now they’re back. they’re sitting there on the kitchen counter like it never happened
theyre moving. THEYRE MOVING THE BAGS ARE MOVING
Get out of there!!!!! PLEASE YOU ARE SCARING ME
but its my baby. what if she’s back. what if my baby’s back
what if my baby’s still alive
talia listen to me. its evil. don’t go to the bags. just get out of the house. leave your phone. PLEASE!
my baby im so sorry my baby
[FWD]: unknown sender: come get me mommy
no Talia don’t. ive got a bad feeling. you’re not right. you’re hallucinating.
i have to see my baby
she’s in the bags. its her. she’s here.
everyone's worried sick about you - me included
you don’t need to talk about talia right now but i’m here for you
i am your big brother after all - that doesn’t change
i had been texting with her when it happened
but they found her suffocated in a black garbage bag!!
maybe she just wanted to be with her mama
